repository-code: https://github.com/fxops-ai/AI-acceptable-use-policy
abstract: >
  A customizable AI Acceptable Use Policy and governance framework for US
  enterprises. Covers four functional domains: compliance and data governance,
  HR handbook provisions for AI users, IT and information security controls,
  and legal protections for intellectual property and confidential information.
  Draws from NIST AI RMF (2025), ISO/IEC 42001:2022, the Defend Trade Secrets
  Act, CCPA, and emerging US federal AI policy. Includes a customization
  questionnaire and sample contractual language. MIT licensed and free to adapt.
